Did you ever see that movie, The Paper?

36:19.818 --> 36:22.961
Yeah, sure.

36:23.061 --> 36:24.123
I love that.

36:24.143 --> 36:26.285
Yeah, I love that.

36:26.305 --> 36:36.017
I think of all the newspaper movies I've seen, it really does seem to be Michael Keaton.

36:36.037 --> 36:36.377
Michael Keaton.

36:36.457 --> 36:37.919
Did you see that, Mr. Winchester?

36:37.939 --> 36:38.179
Yeah, I did.

36:38.199 --> 36:39.261
It's very good, isn't it?

36:39.281 --> 36:41.243
You know, the comedy movie may come up.

36:41.223 --> 36:51.281
Which one?

36:51.301 --> 36:51.361
No.

36:51.381 --> 36:51.783
Is Redford doing it?

36:51.803 --> 36:52.506
No, I think he's... Redford passed?

36:52.526 --> 36:52.887
I think he passed.

